00:02:29.140  --> 00:02:30.650 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
身處於這種環境


00:02:30.650  --> 00:02:32.860 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
為了保護自身的心靈


00:02:32.860  --> 00:02:35.940 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
往往會製造出頑強的人格面具


00:02:40.660  --> 00:02:44.280 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
