00:02:47.120  --> 00:02:47.950 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
有的時候


00:02:48.329  --> 00:02:52.420 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
甚至頑強到會讓人以為是不同的人格


00:02:54.340  --> 00:02:55.380 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
白銀


00:02:55.960  --> 00:02:57.170 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
不, 會長


00:02:57.550  --> 00:03:00.260 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
我們來談談上次發生的那件事吧


00:03:00.260  --> 00:03:01.130 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
來了


00:03:01.130  --> 00:03:05.640 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
會長對我們之間的關係有什麼想法呢


00:03:07.060  --> 00:03:11.060 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
說是學生會的同伴也顯得乏味


00:03:11.730  --> 00:03:14.610 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
但說是朋友感覺又怪怪的


00:03:16.020  --> 00:03:18.990 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
都走到這個地步了…或許…


00:03:20.780  --> 00:03:24.410 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
可以算是情侶…之類的了吧?


00:03:24.700  --> 00:03:26.490 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
說是情侶也太離譜了吧


00:03:26.490  --> 00:03:28.370 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
真的假的?


00:03:28.910  --> 00:03:31.540 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
只是接了個吻就擺起男朋友架子了嗎


00:03:32.000  --> 00:03:34.040 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
覺得接過吻就算是情侶


00:03:34.040  --> 00:03:35.840 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
又不是小孩子了


00:03:35.840  --> 00:03:36.540 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
不過


00:03:36.540  --> 00:03:39.630 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
會長會想到那裡去也是沒辦法的事


00:03:40.380  --> 00:03:44.300 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
我打從一開始就知道會長對我有意思了


00:03:45.350  --> 00:03:47.640 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
那四宮妳自己又是怎麼想的


00:03:47.640  --> 00:03:49.520 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
妳是抱著什麼念頭和我接吻的?


00:03:49.520  --> 00:03:51.480 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
妳是因為喜歡我才和我接吻的吧?


00:03:51.480  --> 00:03:52.480 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
既然如此…


00:03:52.980  --> 00:03:55.100 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
請不要因為接了一兩次吻


00:03:55.100  --> 00:03:56.190 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
就大驚小怪的


00:03:57.480  --> 00:03:58.520 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
那點小事


00:03:58.520  --> 00:04:00.940 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
只要興致來了任誰我都會接受的


00:04:01.650  --> 00:04:04.160 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
不然要不要現在就來試試呢


00:04:05.950  --> 00:04:06.990 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
接吻


00:04:27.180  --> 00:04:29.640 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
一個大男人擺出什麼等著被吻的表情


00:04:29.640  --> 00:04:30.560 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
真是噁心


00:04:30.810  --> 00:04:33.310 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
不, 我只是以為…


00:04:33.730  --> 00:04:36.230 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
以為一定又要被妳強吻了


00:04:36.230  --> 00:04:40.820 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
那個吻已經深深刻印在白銀的腦中了


00:04:41.190  --> 00:04:43.990 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
剛才的確是很那個沒錯


00:04:43.990  --> 00:04:45.780 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
但妳也用不著打我吧


00:04:46.110  --> 00:04:47.240 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
不好意思


00:04:47.240  --> 00:04:48.909 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
對做事溫吞的人施以懲罰調教


00:04:48.909  --> 00:04:50.370 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
是我們四宮家的作風


00:04:50.790  --> 00:04:52.040 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
總而言之


00:04:52.040  --> 00:04:55.460 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
我不打算和沒出息的男人交往


00:04:56.710  --> 00:04:57.880 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
今天就先到此為止


00:04:58.130  --> 00:04:59.090 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
再見


00:05:00.880  --> 00:05:01.500 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
哎呀?


00:05:02.010  --> 00:05:04.550 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
本來想打電話叫人來接我的


00:05:05.260  --> 00:05:07.720 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
智慧型手機的續航力就是不夠持久


00:05:08.260  --> 00:05:10.050 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
那我就走路回去好了


00:05:10.760  --> 00:05:13.100 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
四宮妳自己走夜路回去不好吧


00:05:14.520  --> 00:05:16.310 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
那麼你打算怎麼做呢


00:05:21.070  --> 00:05:23.530 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
四宮到底發生什麼事了


00:05:24.280  --> 00:05:27.240 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
直到昨天感覺明明都還很不錯的


00:05:27.610  --> 00:05:29.530 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
剛才卻突然說不想和我交往了


00:05:30.330  --> 00:05:32.290 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
現在又要我陪她一起走回家


00:05:33.159  --> 00:05:36.159 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
還有這個冷若冰霜的表情


00:05:36.750  --> 00:05:37.790 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
簡直就像


00:05:37.790  --> 00:05:41.210 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
以前那個拒人於千里之外的四宮啊


00:05:42.130  --> 00:05:44.420 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
她一定是發生什麼事了


00:05:45.260  --> 00:05:47.590 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
是留學的事被家人說了什麼嗎?


00:05:47.930  --> 00:05:49.550 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
還是交往的事被反對了?


00:05:50.510  --> 00:05:53.430 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
該不會是她已經有未婚夫了吧


00:05:53.430  --> 00:05:56.180 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
所以她現在才會表示無法和我交往


00:05:56.850  --> 00:05:58.060 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
快想辦法察覺啊


00:05:58.060  --> 00:06:01.060 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
四宮一定是正在對我發出某種信號


00:06:01.060  --> 00:06:03.110 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
我真羨慕男人


00:06:04.900  --> 00:06:07.650 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
就算像這樣手插著口袋走路


00:06:07.650  --> 00:06:09.780 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
也不會被任何人指責


00:06:12.580  --> 00:06:14.540 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
指尖好冷啊


00:06:14.740  --> 00:06:17.250 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
四宮正一邊思考男尊女卑的事情


00:06:17.250  --> 00:06:18.710 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
一邊嘆氣


00:06:18.960  --> 00:06:21.580 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
說到將人當成物品看待的四宮家


00:06:21.580  --> 00:06:23.000 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
和男尊女卑有關的事情


00:06:23.500  --> 00:06:25.130 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
果然是未婚夫嗎?


00:06:25.420  --> 00:06:28.670 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
白銀的內心受到相當大的打擊


00:06:28.670  --> 00:06:31.550 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
四宮…妳到底希望我怎麼做


00:06:31.840  --> 00:06:33.390 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
快把妳的想法告訴我吧


00:06:33.390  --> 00:06:35.060 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
真的好冷喔


00:06:35.600  --> 00:06:38.600 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
再這樣下去連內心都會結凍的


00:06:38.890  --> 00:06:41.690 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
真羨慕某人的手看起來暖呼呼的


00:06:44.320  --> 00:06:47.360 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
她是希望我伸出援手給她溫暖的救援嗎


00:06:48.070  --> 00:06:49.900 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
這就是四宮給我的SOS信號


00:06:50.240  --> 00:06:50.990 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
我得…


00:06:52.120  --> 00:06:54.080 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
我得快想想辦法才行


00:07:01.210  --> 00:07:02.170 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
會長你…


00:07:04.210  --> 00:07:07.460 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
連護送一個女孩子這種事都做不好嗎


00:07:08.630  --> 00:07:10.130 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
真是可愛呢


00:07:27.980  --> 00:07:29.150 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
沒出息


00:07:38.120  --> 00:07:41.159 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
有夠搞笑的


00:07:42.960  --> 00:07:47.380 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
