00:07:51.720  --> 00:07:53.760 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
今天不用綁頭髮了


00:07:54.260  --> 00:07:55.010 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
唉呀


00:07:55.680  --> 00:07:56.470 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
做為代替


00:07:56.470  --> 00:07:59.220 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
嫂子之前送的香水現在還有剩嗎?


00:07:59.520  --> 00:08:00.480 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
唉呀唉呀


00:08:01.600  --> 00:08:03.440 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
84隻…


00:08:03.980  --> 00:08:06.400 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
85隻羊…


00:08:07.150  --> 00:08:09.650 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
86隻羊…


