00:09:23.270  --> 00:09:24.430 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
要再幫你化妝嗎?


00:09:24.430  --> 00:09:26.520 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
不, 請饒了我吧


00:09:27.060  --> 00:09:28.270 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
真遺憾


00:09:29.020  --> 00:09:31.650 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
咦? 她今天心情不錯?


00:09:32.320  --> 00:09:33.780 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
四宮, 早安


00:09:37.490  --> 00:09:37.860 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
轉頭


00:09:37.860  --> 00:09:39.120 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
為什麼無視我?


00:09:39.530  --> 00:09:42.740 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
關於要在我家舉辦的聖誕派對呀


00:09:43.580  --> 00:09:44.950 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
首先是乾杯


00:09:44.950  --> 00:09:46.790 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
- 石上你不覺得四宮
- 喝的當然是無酒精飲料囉


00:09:46.790  --> 00:09:48.210 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
- 今天怪怪的嗎
- 是啊


00:09:48.210  --> 00:09:50.790 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
- 不會啊? 她對我的態度和往常一樣吧
- 交換禮物就安排到後面再進行


00:09:50.790  --> 00:09:52.040 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
- 不會啊? 她對我的態度和往常一樣吧
- 這樣很好啊


00:09:52.040  --> 00:09:52.960 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
然後呀


00:09:52.960  --> 00:09:56.550 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
