00:18:37.650  --> 00:18:40.200 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
輝夜大人比平常還聰明100倍


00:18:42.070  --> 00:18:44.620 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
這是關於我朋友的事


00:18:45.700  --> 00:18:47.000 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
女方當時這麼說


00:18:47.000  --> 00:18:48.500 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
"接吻這點小事興致來了"


00:18:48.500  --> 00:18:49.750 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
"任誰我都會接受"


00:18:49.750  --> 00:18:51.630 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
"不然要不要現在就來試試呢?"


00:18:52.000  --> 00:18:54.380 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
沒有人這樣的吧


00:18:56.090  --> 00:18:57.760 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
聽起來真是可愛呢


00:18:58.260  --> 00:19:01.010 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
我好像能理解那個女孩的心情喔


00:19:02.550  --> 00:19:04.680 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
興致來了任誰都會接受?


00:19:05.470  --> 00:19:08.770 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
這很明顯是在用強硬的語氣掩飾真心話


00:19:09.270  --> 00:19:10.270 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
真心話?


00:19:10.730  --> 00:19:13.440 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
"能讓我產生接吻念頭的人只有你"的


00:19:13.440  --> 00:19:14.440 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
真心話


00:19:14.440  --> 00:19:15.770 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
如果再進一步分析的話


00:19:15.770  --> 00:19:17.280 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
那女孩的真心話是


00:19:17.690  --> 00:19:19.740 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
我希望會長能主動吻我


00:19:21.410  --> 00:19:22.910 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
應該要怎麼做才好


00:19:22.910  --> 00:19:25.830 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
為了讓會長主動吻我


00:19:25.830  --> 00:19:27.240 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
我已經試過很多方法了


00:19:27.240  --> 00:19:28.950 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
卻都沒有效果, 很傷腦筋


00:19:28.950  --> 00:19:31.750 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
讓會長主動親吻?


00:19:31.750  --> 00:19:32.460 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
是啊


00:19:32.920  --> 00:19:34.170 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
吻輝夜大人?


00:19:34.710  --> 00:19:35.880 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
我不就是這麼說的嗎


00:19:35.880  --> 00:19:37.130 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
為什麼?


00:19:37.380  --> 00:19:38.840 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
妳明明早就注意到了


00:19:39.510  --> 00:19:41.550 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
問這種問題真是壞心眼


00:19:43.260  --> 00:19:49.140 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
那當然是因為我…喜歡會長的關係啊


00:19:49.140  --> 00:19:50.600 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
輝…


00:19:50.600  --> 00:19:52.100 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
小輝夜!


00:19:52.100  --> 00:19:53.900 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
為什麼又變回這種稱呼方式


00:19:54.310  --> 00:19:55.150 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
不過


00:19:55.150  --> 00:19:57.270 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
想不到您會這麼乾脆地就承認呢


00:19:57.610  --> 00:20:01.030 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
我已經承認自己對會長懷有情愫了


00:20:01.030  --> 00:20:02.240 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
懷有情愫


00:20:02.530  --> 00:20:03.240 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
因為喜歡他


00:20:03.240  --> 00:20:05.200 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
自然會希望他能主動吻我吧


00:20:05.700  --> 00:20:07.830 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
我希望他能用雙手緊緊擁抱我


00:20:07.830  --> 00:20:09.580 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
如果他進一步要求更多


00:20:09.580  --> 00:20:10.620 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
我應該也會容許…


00:20:10.620  --> 00:20:12.710 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
我懂了, 您說的我都懂了


00:20:15.420  --> 00:20:17.420 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
總之如果希望他吻您的話


00:20:17.420  --> 00:20:20.340 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
將您的心意直接傳達給他不就好了嗎


00:20:20.960  --> 00:20:22.170 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
這點我辦不到


00:20:22.800  --> 00:20:23.630 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
為什麼


00:20:25.640  --> 00:20:27.350 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
每次只要面對會長


00:20:28.760  --> 00:20:30.810 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
我不知為何就是無法坦率


00:20:31.020  --> 00:20:32.730 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
我懂!


00:20:32.980  --> 00:20:33.890 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
就是說啊


00:20:33.890  --> 00:20:35.150 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
在喜歡的人面前


00:20:35.150  --> 00:20:36.810 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
都會忍不住表現得很冷淡


00:20:37.150  --> 00:20:40.730 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
不, 那種態度光用冷淡就能解釋嗎


00:20:41.240  --> 00:20:43.530 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
我也已經做過各種努力了


00:20:44.030  --> 00:20:47.200 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
像是一直喊冷暗示他牽我的手


00:20:47.200  --> 00:20:50.040 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
她走在我身旁時不斷地在表達不滿啊


00:20:50.290  --> 00:20:52.160 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
像今天還擦了香水


00:20:52.160  --> 00:20:53.790 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
然後還一直逃避


00:20:53.790  --> 00:20:56.210 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
其實我連找他講話都覺得難為情


00:20:56.210  --> 00:20:58.040 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
和她打招呼卻又視而不見


00:20:58.040  --> 00:20:59.800 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
體諒她的心情啊!


00:21:00.210  --> 00:21:03.590 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
算我拜託了, 男方要體諒她的心情啊


00:21:03.590  --> 00:21:05.550 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
連我自己聽了都覺得難受了


00:21:05.550  --> 00:21:07.640 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
拜託他理解一下啊


00:21:08.300  --> 00:21:09.390 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
話說回來


00:21:09.390  --> 00:21:12.020 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
那個人和我完全是相同的類型


00:21:12.350  --> 00:21:14.770 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
和她共鳴的程度強烈到讓人害怕


00:21:15.140  --> 00:21:17.480 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
說她是親戚我大概也會相…


00:21:19.860  --> 00:21:20.770 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
剛才說的


00:21:21.280  --> 00:21:24.570 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
該不會是御行和輝夜姨婆間的事吧


00:21:25.990  --> 00:21:28.200 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
我從之前就一直覺得很可疑了


00:21:28.200  --> 00:21:30.160 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
你們兩個進展到什麼地步了


00:21:30.160  --> 00:21:32.080 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
這…


00:21:32.450  --> 00:21:34.830 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
我們在文化祭做過大人的接吻了


00:21:36.080  --> 00:21:38.920 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
虧我還以為你是同伴, 竟然先偷跑


00:21:38.920  --> 00:21:40.790 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
我不想知道這種事啊


00:21:41.380  --> 00:21:42.590 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
大人的接吻


00:21:43.210  --> 00:21:44.670 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
大概40秒?


00:21:44.970  --> 00:21:47.220 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
點與點連成線了


00:21:47.510  --> 00:21:50.550 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
但是, 那個吻失敗了


00:21:50.970  --> 00:21:52.220 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
是這樣嗎


00:21:52.640  --> 00:21:55.480 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
柏木同學初次接吻是什麼樣的狀況


00:21:56.020  --> 00:21:57.600 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
反過來問我嗎


00:21:58.100  --> 00:21:58.980 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
(某個夏天…)


00:21:58.980  --> 00:22:00.690 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
約會完回家的路上


00:22:01.270  --> 00:22:03.030 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
在等紅綠燈的時候


00:22:05.610  --> 00:22:06.990 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
他就突然…


00:22:08.950  --> 00:22:10.870 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
我不想知道這種事啊


00:22:11.280  --> 00:22:12.740 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
真是美妙呢


00:22:12.740  --> 00:22:15.200 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
但他是在超商前突然吻我的耶


00:22:15.620  --> 00:22:17.290 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
根本一點也不浪漫


00:22:17.750  --> 00:22:19.040 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
這樣就夠了


00:22:19.880  --> 00:22:21.920 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
我也比較喜歡大家都在做的那種


00:22:22.250  --> 00:22:24.800 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
這世界上隨處可見的接吻


00:22:27.630  --> 00:22:28.930 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
我只不過是


00:22:30.760  --> 00:22:32.600 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
想談一場普通的戀愛


00:22:40.650  --> 00:22:42.150 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
四宮她…


00:22:43.730  --> 00:22:46.820 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
是怎麼看待我的呢


00:23:10.050  --> 00:23:11.640 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
"冰輝夜"


00:23:12.010  --> 00:23:15.310 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
是四宮輝夜具有的多面性之一


00:23:15.930  --> 00:23:20.270 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
那是任誰都有的對他人的警戒心


00:23:20.270  --> 00:23:21.310 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
而同時


00:23:21.690  --> 00:23:25.070 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
也是膽小的愛戀之心


00:23:27.070  --> 00:23:28.320 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
我明明那麼喜歡你


00:23:39.200  --> 00:23:40.910 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
今天的勝敗結果


00:23:41.540  --> 00:23:45.250 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
四宮輝夜敗北


00:23:46.090  --> 00:23:48.210 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
我被御行背叛了


00:23:48.630  --> 00:23:50.800 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
我能依靠的人果然就只有優了


00:23:50.800  --> 00:23:52.470 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
被不妙的人在不妙的時機


00:23:52.470  --> 00:23:54.930 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
講著不妙的話抱過來了!


00:23:56.850  --> 00:24:00.020 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
(昔日的兩人…)


00:24:16.490  --> 00:24:18.330 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
對不起


00:24:18.790  --> 00:24:26.840 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
將一切都怪罪於溫柔的你


00:24:28.840  --> 00:24:33.550 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
那困擾的側臉


00:24:34.380  --> 00:24:39.760 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
相信只有我可以化解


00:24:40.140  --> 00:24:41.890 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
在你的身邊


00:24:41.890  --> 00:24:45.980 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
心中彷彿已經快要凍僵的思念


00:24:46.310  --> 00:24:51.990 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
今天一定要好好率直地


00:24:52.650  --> 00:24:55.660 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
傳達給你知道


00:24:55.860  --> 00:25:00.290 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
我們總是能在迷惘之中


00:25:00.290  --> 00:25:03.120 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
邂逅彼此


00:25:03.120  --> 00:25:04.710 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
那所有的一切


00:25:04.710  --> 00:25:08.000 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
全是只屬於我的心意


00:25:08.000  --> 00:25:12.590 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
藏在我的心靈筆記中


00:25:12.590  --> 00:25:17.050 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
不論甜美還是苦澀


00:25:17.050  --> 00:25:21.930 position:50% line:94% align:middle 
願你能擁抱這一切

